---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
---
<Layout title="The Roadies (Groomsmen)">
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 w-full mt-8">
    <a href="/backstage" class="text-amber-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-amber-500 mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back to Hub</a>
    
    <h1 class="text-6xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase">The Roadies</h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-bold mb-12">Groomsmen Eyes Only</p>
    
    <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-amber-600 shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">The Pre-Party (Bachelor Weekend)</h2>
      <p class="text-amber-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-4">Dates TBD • Cabin in the Woods</p>
      <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>We're apparently going camping in the middle of nowhere instead of a strip club. Expect cheap beer, a fire pit, and extremely loud music. The best man is handling the Airbnb booking, so venmo him when he texts the group thread.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-zinc-100 shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Suiting Up</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-4">Deadline: September 1st</p>
      <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>We are doing black suits and white shirts, with no tie but a cool lapelle. Click here for a link to the suit. Get your measurements done by September 1st or you're doing security at the door instead of standing on the stage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-emerald-600 shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Day-Of Load-In</h2>
      <p class="text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-4">Call Time: 1:00 PM Sharp</p>
      <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Do not be late. Show up to the venue completely dressed. We are doing groomsmen photos first so we can hit the bar before the ceremony starts. Matt has the rings so guard him with your life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>